    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/ca19014a92034c1d0e6a8427a8918255.avif?t=1729123336\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras_big/ca19014a92034c1d0e6a8427a8918255.avif?t=1729123336 width=800 height=133 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Astrotoons is a party-shooter offering both co-op and PvP modes up to four players. Cooperate with friends to complete missions and escape, or compete against each other in exciting PvP matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a3a31e50b3e73255ea9ae1461a78c1fd.poster.avif?t=1729123336\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a3a31e50b3e73255ea9ae1461a78c1fd.webm?t=1729123336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a3a31e50b3e73255ea9ae1461a78c1fd.mp4?t=1729123336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/d00c1522657142a3103c7898767f09b0.webp?t=1729123336\" width=759 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot your way through hordes of enemies using a wide range of powerful weapons and tools, but choose carefully! some enemies may have different reactions to certain weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/be128953950f14f97e92433eab2946f2.webp?t=1729123336\" width=759 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve every objective in order to complete the current mission and earn your extraction back to the ship. <i>(extraction may be more difficult than it seems, do not give up!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/4486047fc9c7edde96840358fb7c4fed.webp?t=1729123336\" width=759 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the role you play in your team by picking the right tool or weapon to solve the current situation you're in. Don't get stuck in one role or your team will perish.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/05a4f07ea997f0480abe950555546335.webp?t=1729123336\" width=759 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cooperate with your teammates or compete with each other in a wide variety of PvP modes with lots of different arenas and win conditions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a5fbc56807bbf3bfcb1e55d4971e20f0.poster.avif?t=1729123336\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a5fbc56807bbf3bfcb1e55d4971e20f0.webm?t=1729123336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186080/extras/a5fbc56807bbf3bfcb1e55d4971e20f0.mp4?t=1729123336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
